    {
      "id": "optimistic_5_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_5",
      "description": "Step into luxury with this absolutely flawless vehicle! This car is in true mint condition, looking and driving exactly like it just left the showroom floor. From the pristine interior to the sparkling exterior and smooth performance, it's a perfect find for anyone seeking excellence. Don't miss out on this pristine gem!",
